<h1 id="appendix-a-è¡Œåˆ—ã®ãƒˆãƒ¬ãƒ¼ã‚¹ã®å…¬å¼-33å¼ã®è¨¼æ˜">Appendix A: è¡Œåˆ—ã®ãƒˆãƒ¬ãƒ¼ã‚¹ã®å…¬å¼ (3.3)å¼ã®è¨¼æ˜</h1>

<p>é€”ä¸­ã§å‡ºã¦ããŸè¡Œåˆ—ã®ãƒˆãƒ¬ãƒ¼ã‚¹ã«ã¤ã„ã¦æˆã‚Šç«‹ã¤å…¬å¼ã‚’è¨¼æ˜ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚ãã®ãŸã‚ã«ä»¥ä¸‹ã®æ‰‹é †ã§ç¤ºã—ã¦ã„ãã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<h2 id="å¯æ›å‰‡">å¯æ›å‰‡</h2>

\[\mathrm{Tr} (AB) 
= \sum_{i=1}^n (AB)_{ii} 
= \sum_{i=1}^n \left( \sum_{j=1}^n A_{ij} B_{ji} \right) 
= \sum_{j=1}^n \left( \sum_{i=1}^n B_{ji} A_{ij} \right) 
= \mathrm{Tr} (BA) \tag{A.1}\]

<p>ãŒæˆã‚Šç«‹ã¡ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<h2 id="è¡Œåˆ—ã®ãƒˆãƒ¬ãƒ¼ã‚¹ãŒãã®è¡Œåˆ—ã®å›ºæœ‰å€¤ã®ç·å’Œã¨ãªã‚‹">è¡Œåˆ—ã®ãƒˆãƒ¬ãƒ¼ã‚¹ãŒã€ãã®è¡Œåˆ—ã®å›ºæœ‰å€¤ã®ç·å’Œã¨ãªã‚‹</h2>

<p>è¡Œåˆ—\(A\)ã‚’å¯¾è§’åŒ–ã™ã‚‹ãŸã‚ã«ç”¨ã„ã‚‹æ­£å‰‡è¡Œåˆ—ã‚’\(\Lambda\)ã¨ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\Lambda^{-1} A \Lambda 
= C \tag{A.2}\]

<p>å³è¾ºã®\(C\)ã¯\(A\)ã‚’å¯¾è§’åŒ–ã—ã¦ç”Ÿã¾ã‚ŒãŸå¯¾è§’è¡Œåˆ—ã§ã™ã€‚\(A\)ã®å›ºæœ‰å€¤ã‚’\(\lambda_1, \lambda_2, \cdots, \lambda_n\)ã¨ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[C = \left( 
\begin{array}{cccc}
\lambda_1 &amp; &amp; &amp; \mathbf{0} \\
 &amp; \lambda_2 &amp; &amp; \\
 &amp; &amp; \ddots &amp; \\
 \mathbf{0} &amp; &amp; &amp; \lambda_n
\end{array} \right) \tag{A.3}\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚(A.2)ã®ä¸¡è¾ºã®ãƒˆãƒ¬ãƒ¼ã‚¹ã‚’å–ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\mathrm{Tr} (\Lambda^{-1} A \Lambda) 
= \mathrm{Tr} (C) 
= \sum_{i=1}^n \lambda_i\]

<p>ä¸€æ–¹ã§ä¸Šå¼ã®æœ€å·¦è¾ºã¯ã€å…ˆã»ã©ã®(A.1)å¼ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã¦</p>

\[\mathrm{Tr} (\Lambda^{-1} A \Lambda) 
= \mathrm{Tr} ( A \Lambda^{-1} \Lambda) 
= \mathrm{Tr} (A)\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚ä»¥ä¸Šã‚’åˆã‚ã›ã¦</p>

\[\mathrm{Tr} (A) 
= \sum_{i=1}^n \lambda_i \tag{A.4}\]

<h2 id="é€”ä¸­ã®å…¬å¼ã®è¨¼æ˜">é€”ä¸­ã®å…¬å¼ã®è¨¼æ˜</h2>

<p>ã“ã‚Œã‚‰ã‹ã‚‰ã€æ±‚ã‚ã‚‹å½¢ã®è¨¼æ˜ã‚’ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚(A.2)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[A 
= \Lambda C \Lambda^{-1} \ \Longrightarrow \ 
e^A 
= e^{\Lambda C \Lambda^{-1}}\]

<p>å®šç¾©ã«å¾“ã£ã¦ã€ã“ã‚Œã®å³è¾ºã‚’å’Œã®å½¢ã§è¡¨ç¾ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[e^{\Lambda C \Lambda^{-1}} 
= I + \Lambda C \Lambda^{-1} + \frac{(\Lambda C \Lambda^{-1})}{2!} + \cdots\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§\((\Lambda C \Lambda^{-1}) = \Lambda C \Lambda^{-1}\Lambda C \Lambda^{-1} = \Lambda C^2 \Lambda^{-1}\)ãªã©ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[e^{\Lambda C \Lambda^{-1}} 
= \Lambda \Lambda^{-1} + \Lambda C \Lambda^{-1} + \frac{\Lambda C^2 \Lambda^{-1}}{2!} + \cdots 
= \Lambda \left( I + C + \frac{C^2}{2!} + \cdots \right) \Lambda^{-1} 
= \Lambda e^C \Lambda^{-1}\]

<p>ã‚ˆã£ã¦</p>

\[e^A 
= \Lambda e^C \Lambda^{-1} \ \Longrightarrow \Â 
\mathrm{det} (e^A) 
= \mathrm{det} (\Lambda e^C \Lambda^{-1}) 
= \mathrm{det} (\Lambda) \mathrm{det} (e^C) \mathrm{det} (\Lambda^{-1}) 
= \mathrm{det} (e^C)\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã§(A.3)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[e^C 
= I + C + \frac{C^2}{2!} + \cdots 
= \left( \begin{array}{cccc}
1 + \lambda_1 + \frac{\lambda_1^2}{2!} + \cdots &amp; &amp; &amp; \\
&amp; 1 + \lambda_2 + \frac{\lambda_2^2}{2!} + \cdots &amp; &amp; \\
&amp; &amp; \ddots &amp; \\
&amp; &amp; &amp; 1 + \lambda_n + \frac{\lambda_n^2}{2!} + \cdots 
\end{array} \right)
= \left( \begin{array}{cccc}
e^{\lambda_1} &amp; &amp; &amp; \\
&amp; e^{\lambda_2}&amp; &amp; \\
&amp; &amp; \ddots &amp; \\
&amp; &amp; &amp; e^{\lambda_n}
\end{array} \right)\]

<p>ã¨ã‚ã‹ã‚‹ã®ã§</p>

\[\mathrm{det} (e^C) 
= e^{\lambda_1} e^{\lambda_2} \cdots e^{\lambda_n} 
= e^{\lambda_1 + \lambda_2 + \cdots + \lambda_n} 
\underbrace{=}_{(A.4)} e^{\mathrm{Tr} (A)} \ \Longrightarrow \Â 
\therefore \ \mathrm{det} (e^A) 
= e^{\mathrm{Tr} (A)} \tag{A.5}\]

<p>ãŒæˆç«‹ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã‚ã‹ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚(A.5)å¼ã®ä¸¡è¾ºã®logã‚’å–ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\log [\mathrm{det} (e^A)] 
= \mathrm{Tr} (A)\]

<p>ãã—ã¦\(A = A\log e = \log e^A\)ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚Œã°</p>

\[\log [\mathrm{det} (e^A)] 
= \mathrm{Tr} [\log e^{A}]\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ä¸¡è¾ºã«\(e^A\)ãŒç¾ã‚Œã¦ã„ã‚‹ã®ã§ã€\(e^A \rightarrow \lambda I - A\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ç½®ãæ›ãˆã‚Œã°ã€(3.3)å¼ã«ä¸€è‡´ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<h1 id="appendix-b-é€”ä¸­ã®äºˆæƒ³ãŒæ­£ã—ã„ã“ã¨ã®è¨¼æ˜">Appendix B: é€”ä¸­ã®äºˆæƒ³ãŒæ­£ã—ã„ã“ã¨ã®è¨¼æ˜</h1>

\[P(y_\mu^{a=1 \sim n}) 
= \int_{-\infty}^\infty \prod_{i=1}^N dx_{\mu i} \exp \left( - \frac{1}{2} \sum_{i=1}^N x_{\mu i}^2 \right) \prod_{a=1}^n \delta \left( y_\mu^a - \frac{1}{\sqrt{N}} \sum_{i=1}^N x_{\mu i} u_{ia} \right)\]

<p>ãƒ‡ãƒ«ã‚¿é–¢æ•°ã®ãƒ•ãƒ¼ãƒªã‚¨ç©åˆ†è¡¨ç¤ºã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[P(y_\mu^{a=1 \sim n}) 
= \int_{-\infty}^\infty d\tilde{y}_\mu \int d{\bf{x}}_\mu \exp \left( -\frac{1}{2} \sum_{i=1}^N x_{\mu i}^2 + i \sum_{a=1}^n \tilde{y}_{\mu a} \left( y_{\mu a} - \frac{1}{\sqrt{N}} \sum_{i=1}^N x_{\mu i} u_{ia} \right) \right)\]

<p>ã“ã®å¼ã«ç¾ã‚ŒãŸ\(e\)ã®è‚©ã«ã¤ã„ã¦æ•´ç†ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚</p>

\[-\frac{1}{2} \sum_{i=1}^N \left( x_{\mu i} - i \sum_a \frac{\tilde{y}_{\mu a}}{\sqrt{N}} u_{ia} \right)^2 - \frac{1}{2N} \sum_{i=1}^N \left( \sum_{a=1}^n \tilde{y}_{\mu a} u_{ia}\right)^2 + i \sum_a y_{\mu a} \tilde{y}_{\mu a}\]

<p>ã‚ˆã£ã¦ã‚¬ã‚¦ã‚¹ç©åˆ†ãŒã§ãã¦</p>

\[P(y_\mu^{a=1 \sim n}) 
\propto \int d\tilde{y}_{\mu a} \exp \left( -\frac{1}{2} \sum_{a, b} \tilde{y}_{\mu a} \left( \frac{1}{N} \sum_{i=1} u_{ia} u_{ib}\right) \tilde{y}_{\mu b} + i \sum_{a=1}^n \tilde{y}_{\mu a} y_{\mu a} \right)  
\propto \exp \left( - \frac{1}{2} \sum_{a, b} y_{\mu a} [Q^{-1}]_{a b} y_{\mu b} \right)\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã‚ˆã£ã¦\(y_{\mu a}\)ãŒå†ã³ã‚¬ã‚¦ã‚¹åˆ†å¸ƒã«å¾“ã£ã¦ã„ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã‚ã‹ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã“ã‹ã‚‰å¹³å‡ã¯\([y_{\mu a}] = 0\), åˆ†æ•£ã¯\([y_{\mu a} y_{\mu b}] = [Q]_{ab} = q^{ab}\)ã¨ãªã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã‚ã‹ã‚Šã¾ã—ãŸã€‚</p>

